  "status": "active",
  "version": 1,
  "summary": "Use Nunito Sans, Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; load Nunito Sans via @font-face/Google Fonts; body \u226516px, line height \u2265150% (160% light on dark); 14px secondary sparingly; 12px footnotes smaller and distinct."
